X-To: Richard Shapiro <Richard Shapiro/NA/Enron@Enron>, skean <skean@enron.com>, Susan J Mara <Susan J Mara/NA/Enron@ENRON>, Harry Kingerski <Harry Kingerski/Enron@EnronXGate>, James D Steffes <James D Steffes/NA/Enron@Enron>, Linda Robertson <Linda Robertson/NA/Enron@ENRON>, Susan M Landwehr <Susan M Landwehr/Enron@EnronXGate>, mpalmer <mpalmer@enron.com>, Karen Denne <Karen Denne/Enron@EnronXGate>, Janel Guerrero <Janel Guerrero/Enron@EnronXGate>, Paul Kaufman <Paul Kaufman/Enron@EnronXGate>
X-cc: 
