Subject: California Assembly Releases "Modified MOU" for Edison
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: Jeff Dasovich
X-To: David W Delainey, Greg Whalley, Louise Kitchen, Jeremy Blachman, John J Lavorato, Christopher F Calger, Tim Belden, Phillip K Allen, Richard Shapiro, Kristin Walsh, Michael Tribolet, Janet R Dietrich, James D Steffes, skean@enron.com, mpalmer@enron.com, Karen Denne, Harry Kingerski, Susan J Mara, jdasovic@enron.com, Linda Robertson, Janel Guerrero, Susan M Landwehr, Paul Kaufman, Marty Sunde, Vicki Sharp, Robert C Williams, Mike D Smith
